      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Second比较简单，里面只有一个TransactionQueue。Third也是复合状态，包含PaymentGateway，并且PaymentGateway要连回3rd状态，最后3rd还要闭环回到AuthVault。",
      "elements_involved": [
