      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "现在细化First复合状态。它内部要有1st状态，1st再连到innerFirst，innerFirst再连到2nd。innerFirst本身也是个复合状态，里面嵌套1st1st和1st2nd两个子状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
