      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下First的结构层级：外层是First复合状态，里面有1st；1st连到innerFirst；innerFirst内部再嵌套1st1st和1st2nd，同时innerFirst还要连到2nd。对吗？",
